1. Kralj *stoluje* u dvorcu. (The king *resides* in the castle.)
2. *Kraljevstvo* je bilo pod opsadom neprijatelja. (The *kingdom* was under siege by the enemy.)
3. On je *kralj* šaha u našem klubu. (He is the *king* of chess in our club.)
4. Njihov *kralj* je imao reputaciju okrutnika. (Their *king* had a reputation for being cruel.)
5. Novac nije mogao kupiti sreću *kraljeve* porodice. (Money couldn't buy the happiness of the *king's* family.)
6. *Kraljica* je bila poznata po svom stilu oblačenja. (The *queen* was known for her sense of fashion.)
7. Njegovo visočanstvo *kralj* je bio veoma strog prema svojim podanicima. (His majesty the *king* was very strict with his subjects.)
8. *Kraljevski* bal je okupio mnoge pripadnike aristokratije. (The *royal* ball gathered many aristocrats.)
9. *Kraljevski* potez bio je presudan za ishod bitke. (The *kingly* move was crucial for the outcome of the battle.)
10. Ovaj portret prikazuje *kralja* u punoj raskoši svog kraljevskog plavetnila. (This portrait depicts the *king* in all the splendor of his royal blue.)